<div class="row" id="start-dots">
<div class="col-75">
<div class="section-subtitle text-with-brush masked-text orange">We supported women’s voice and leadership to put gender equality on the agenda – <strong>and kept it there</strong></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-25 text-right">
<div class="button-down_icon"><a class="button-down fade-in-y" href="#feminist-economics"><svg fill="none" height="36" viewbox="0 0 36 36" width="36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M30 18L27.88 15.88L19.5 24.26L19.5 6L16.5 6L16.5 24.26L8.12 15.88L6 18L18 30L30 18Z" fill="black"></path> </svg> </a></div>
</div>
