<div class="col-50 two-columns__left order-2"><img alt="Photo: UN Women/James Ochweri" src="/sites/default/files/assets/annual-reports/2023/assets/img/Kenya_WEE_DonorRecognition_Japan_01_1500px.jpg" />
<div class="footnote">Photo: UN Women/James Ochweri</div>
